data.description: Experience tranquility and ample space on this expansive 2.05-acre corner lot nestled in the highly coveted Cimarron City. Home has a brand-new, top-tier industrial-quality metal roof. This property has space for it all, from recreational vehicles to outdoor equipment, on this generous property. The functional living room features a cozy pellet stove, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for relaxation.The kitchen, designed for both practicality and space, features a charming breakfast nook and offers abundant space for your personal touch and customizations. While this home presents a fantastic opportunity to acquire a unique property, a little tender loving care (TLC) can go a long way in unlocking its full potential. Seize the chance to build equity through personalization and improvements. For those seeking financial assistance in realizing their renovation dreams, we have partnered with reputable lenders ready to provide support through renovation loans.
